<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4576876>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 7. Clostophis multiformis Páll-Gergely & A. Reischütz, new species (NHMW 113273, holotype). A, dorsal view; B, ventral view; C, apertural view; D, lateral view; E, aperture dentition; F, protoconch sculpture; G, sculpture of the ventral side; H, sculpture of body whorl from standard apertural view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4576876/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4576865>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 2. Known distribution of Clostophis species. Empty triangle: Clostophis stochi; inverted empty triangle: C. proboscideus; filled triangle: Clostophis sankeyi; inverted filled triangle: Clostophis koilobasis, new species, and Clostophis incurvus, new species; filled square: Clostophis neglectus; filled diamond: Clostophis platytrochus, new species. Inset map shows the distribution of Clostophis multiformis, new species (circles with labels, see explanation in the text), Clostophis obtusus, new species (empty diamond), and Clostophis infantilis, new species (empty square), east of Thakhek." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4576865/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4576880>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 8. Clostophis multiformis Páll-Gergely & A. Reischütz, new species (NHMW 113274, paratype). A, dorsal view; B, ventral view; C, apertural view; D, lateral view; E, aperture dentition; F, protoconch sculpture; G, sculpture of the ventral side; H, sculpture of body whorl from standard apertural view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4576880/files/figure.png" .

